rows.label: tlk70000027_03_msg0001
rows.name:
What an honor to welcome back
not only Laura-sama, but our
Paragon, Lord Shin, as well.

rows.label: tlk70000027_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Who would have thought I would
be here to witness such a
remarkable event in history?

rows.label: tlk70000027_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Laura-sama, Lord Shin, Prince
Adel! Long may your noble hands
guide the land of Iira!

rows.label: tlk70000027_03_msg0004
rows.name:
This day will remain engraved in my
memory and I shall endeavor to record
your great deeds in Iira's histories!
